      "all_models_close": "Macro aggregate gap between rank 1 and rank 3 is only 0.0222 — confirming that architecture is the binding constraint, not corpus choice, at 1.3B scale.",
      "bleu_range_explanation": "BLEU scores of 7–11 are expected for OPT-1.3b on en-hi. This model was pre-trained primarily on English — Devanagari output quality is limited by the tokenizer and pre-training distribution.",
      "bertscore_most_reliable": "BERTScore using bert-base-multilingual-cased is the most meaningful metric here as it captures semantic similarity in Hindi script better than n-gram metrics like BLEU.",
